<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 06:15:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阿斯顿·马丁的漫步中国大奖赛练习赛最快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/aston-martins-stroll-fastest-chinese-grand-prix-practice-2024-04-19/</link><description>阿斯顿·马丁车队的兰斯·斯特罗尔在周五一级方程式中国大奖赛唯一的自由练习赛中取得了最快圈速，紧随其后的是迈凯轮车队的奥斯卡·皮亚斯特里，因为各车队都在寻求应对五年未曾到过的赛道。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 05:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/aston-martins-stroll-fastest-chinese-grand-prix-practice-2024-04-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国大奖赛练习赛因赛道旁起火而短暂中断</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/chinese-grand-prix-practice-session-briefly-halted-by-track-side-fire-2024-04-19/</link><description>周五，中国大奖赛在上海举行的唯一一场练习赛因赛道旁的一场小火灾而中断，并引发红旗。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 04:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/chinese-grand-prix-practice-session-briefly-halted-by-track-side-fire-2024-04-19/</guid></item><item><title>拜登的关税警告预示着激烈的反华选举战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bidens-tariff-warnings-signal-sharp-anti-china-election-battle-2024-04-19/</link><description>拜登政府威胁对中国征收更多关税是选举年的最新信号，表明无论谁赢得美国总统宝座，与中国的关系都可能会变得更加冷淡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 04:04:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bidens-tariff-warnings-signal-sharp-anti-china-election-battle-2024-04-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国计划在下个月启动新的朝鲜制裁监测制度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-aims-begin-new-north-korea-sanctions-monitoring-regime-by-next-month-2024-04-19/</link><description>美国驻联合国大使周五表示，在俄罗斯和中国阻挠重启监测活动后，她希望找到一种新方法，确保下个月对朝鲜实施制裁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 03:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-aims-begin-new-north-korea-sanctions-monitoring-regime-by-next-month-2024-04-19/</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击伊朗后股市下跌，油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-19/</link><description>亚洲股市和债券收益率周五下跌，而避险货币、黄金和原油则上涨，此前有报道称以色列对伊朗发动一系列持续袭击，加剧了人们对更广泛的中东冲突的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 02:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-19/</guid></item><item><title>北京下令后，苹果从中国应用商店下架 WhatsApp 和 Threads</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-removes-whatsapp-threads-china-app-store-wsj-reports-2024-04-19/</link><description>苹果公司周五表示，在中国政府以国家安全为由下令后，该公司已将 Meta Platforms 的 WhatsApp 和 Threads 从中国的 App Store 下架。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 01:53:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-removes-whatsapp-threads-china-app-store-wsj-reports-2024-04-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国开辟靠近台湾岛屿的新航线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opens-new-air-routes-near-taiwanese-islands-2024-04-19/</link><description>中国航空监管机构周五表示，已开通飞往中国城市厦门和福州的新航线，航线距离​​台湾控制的金门岛和马祖岛非常近，此举可能会激怒台北。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 01:26:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opens-new-air-routes-near-taiwanese-islands-2024-04-19/</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击伊朗的报道引发日元和瑞士法郎的抢购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/surging-dollar-set-weekly-gain-us-data-fed-push-back-rate-cuts-2024-04-19/</link><description>有报道称，以色列在中东冲突升级中袭击了伊朗，周五一波避险情绪席卷市场，投资者纷纷追逐瑞士法郎和日元等传统安全资产。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 01:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/surging-dollar-set-weekly-gain-us-data-fed-push-back-rate-cuts-2024-04-19/</guid></item><item><title>巴布亚新几内亚领导人表示，中国和澳大利亚的访问显示了与大国的“牢固”关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-leader-says-china-australia-visits-show-robust-ties-with-major-2024-04-18/</link><description>巴布亚新几内亚总理詹姆斯·马拉佩周五表示，他期待着中国外交部长和澳大利亚总理在未来几天的访问，这表明了与占其贸易额70%以上的国家的牢固关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-leader-says-china-australia-visits-show-robust-ties-with-major-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：紧张情绪加剧，金融状况收紧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-18/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 21:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛选举计票正在进行，中国批评者苏达尼重新获得席位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/solomon-islands-election-count-underway-china-critic-suidani-regains-seat-2024-04-18/</link><description>所罗门群岛著名的中国批评者、前马莱塔省省长丹尼尔·苏伊达尼（Daniel Suidani）再次当选省议会议员，周五这个太平洋岛国的选举计票工作仍在继续。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 21:32:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/solomon-islands-election-count-underway-china-critic-suidani-regains-seat-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>FBI称中国黑客准备攻击美国基础设施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/fbi-says-chinese-hackers-preparing-attack-us-infrastructure-2024-04-18/</link><description>美国联邦调查局局长克里斯托弗·雷周四表示，与中国政府有关联的黑客已经侵入美国关键基础设施，并正在等待“适当的时机来实施毁灭性打击”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/fbi-says-chinese-hackers-preparing-attack-us-infrastructure-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>美国对乌克兰的援助接近可能通过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-aid-ukraine-moves-closer-possible-passage-2024-04-18/</link><description>美国国会周四接近结束长达数月的僵局，并就向乌克兰、以色列和台湾提供数十亿美元安全援助的立法进行投票，尽管周末投票前对该措施存在激烈争论。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:07:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-aid-ukraine-moves-closer-possible-passage-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>东布罗夫斯基斯表示，欧盟看到中国向俄罗斯供应军民两用零部件的迹象</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/eu-sees-signs-china-supplying-dual-use-components-russia-dombrovskis-says-2024-04-18/</link><description>一位欧盟高级官员周四表示，欧盟看到有迹象表明中国正在向俄罗斯供应可用于制造武器的零部件，并担心如果西方反对俄罗斯发动乌克兰战争的决心减弱，中国可能会更有底气增加出口。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/eu-sees-signs-china-supplying-dual-use-components-russia-dombrovskis-says-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>欧莱雅首席执行官对中国持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-ceo-sets-cautious-tone-china-2024-04-18/</link><description>周四，欧莱雅首席执行官对全球第二大美容市场中国的前景持谨慎态度，尽管这家化妆品制造商公布第一季度中国销售额增长超过 6%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:11:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-ceo-sets-cautious-tone-china-2024-04-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>